text: Fernanda Miranda Paes Leme de Abreu (born 4 June 1983) is a Brazilian actress. She was born in São Paulo. She is known for her television roles in Sandy & Junior, Um Só Coração and Insensato Coração. She has also appeared in movies such as O Homem Que Desafiou o Diabo (2007) and Cilada.com (2011). In March 2020, during the 2019–20 coronavirus pandemic, Paes Leme tested positive for COVID-19. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian movie actors Category:Brazilian television actors Category:Actors from São Paulo
